sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant M as Merchant + Network
    participant Mint as PAR mint()
    participant Eng as Scoring engine
    participant Ver as PAR verify()
    participant Or as Settlement oracle (network-signed)
    U->>M: authorize + settle (AP2 Checkout + Payment mandates)
    M-->>Mint: Closed Checkout Mandate (user+merchant signed)
    M-->>Mint: settlement attestation ref (outcome only)
    Mint->>Mint: hash mandate, attach operator identities + settlement_ref
    Mint-->>Eng: Verified Interaction Record (VIR)
    Eng->>Ver: verify(VIR, mandate_resolver, settlement_resolver)
    Ver->>M: re-resolve checkout mandate by ref (hash check)
    Ver->>Or: resolve settlement attestation (live outcome)
    Or-->>Ver: settled | refunded | charged_back | disputed
    Ver-->>Eng: {verified, well_formed, active, violations}
